author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Margo Price, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when she visited The Turf Club for The Current’s MicroShow series presented by New Belgium Brewing in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Tennessee Song
00:04:32 Since You Put Me Down
00:09:36 This Town Gets Around
00:12:25 It Ain’t Drunk Driving If You’re Riding a Horse
00:15:52 Hurtin’ (On the Bottle)

Musicians
Margo Price – vocals, guitar

Credits
Engineer – Johnny Vince Evans
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan & Leah Garaas
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.

Subscribe to our channel:
http://www.youtube.com/user/893TheCurrent?sub_confirmatio
